$interpreted: Aosta: So your ancestry has finally awakened? Thought you would immediately leave to search for your own species.
Aosta: Didn't think you would still wander around here.
Aosta: Do you really have time to play with me here? Did you not hear the rustling of armor moving straight towards the village?
Aosta: Right, seems like Roger and Kittyeyes have not left there yet...
Kittyeyes: Roger, didn't you promise that we would live a happy life together? Please, return to the real you!
Kittyeyes: Thank goodness. We can't be apart again...
Kittyeyes: Like you promised, we will always be together, happily ever after...
Aosta: What, are you here to ask me about the whereabouts of your fellow Glimmer Wolves?
Aosta: Somewhere in a corner of this world, there is the possibility of a pack existing.
Aosta: A pack of awakened Glimmer Wolves, just like you.
Aosta: The ancient instincts flowing in your blood will naturally guide you to where they are. There's no need for you to ask me.
